# W3 Module Interaction Contracts (v0.1)

## 1. Module Communication Interfaces

### BBX19 -> All Modules
- directive: string (required)
- priority: enum [low, medium, high, critical]
- deadline: timestamp

### Gemini -> System Validation
- validation_request: object (required)
- risk_level: string
- recommendation: string

### DeepSeek -> Pattern Analysis
- pattern_data: object (required)
- analysis_type: enum [structure, behavior, anomaly]
- confidence_score: float

### ChatGPT -> Flow Generation
- flow_spec: object (required)
- complexity: enum [simple, moderate, complex]
- test_cases: array

### Grok -> Narrative Output
- narrative_input: object (required)
- interpretation_level: enum [summary, detailed, technical]
- anomaly_flags: array

### Copilot-Gm -> Orchestration
- orchestration_command: string (required)
- target_modules: array (required)
- execution_context: object

## 2. Cross-Module Message Standards
- message_id: uuid (required)
- source_module: string (required)
- target_module: string (required)
- timestamp: timestamp (required)
- payload: object (required)

## 3. Error Handling
- error_code: string (required)
- error_message: string (required)
- suggested_fix: string
- retry_possible: boolean

## 4. Sync Agreement
- All modules use same contract version
- Version mismatch triggers immediate sync
- Breaking changes require 24-hour notice
